      <p>
        This style guide documents the visual language, components, and patterns used throughout the Adrian Viewpoint website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2>Design Principles</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Consistency</strong> - Uniform visual language across all pages</li>
        <li><strong>Accessibility</strong> - WCAG compliant color contrasts and semantic HTML</li>
        <li><strong>Responsiveness</strong> - Mobile-first responsive design</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

